&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a part time post?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do you value and expect good customer service?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you can answer Yes to the above then we would like to hear from you.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join our Maternity team on a permanent basis.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking to recruit a highly motivated &amp; enthusiastic individual to join the Maternity service.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The post holder will be well presented, highly organised &amp; have excellent customer service skills.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The successful applicant will be required to have an excellent telephone/ communication manner and an understanding of confidentiality. They must be able to work well independently but also be able to work effectively as part of a team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The hours currently available are:-&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tuesday, Wednesday &amp; Thursday 5pm - 10pm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date: 12-Nov-2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
